  "body": "<div id=\"post-view221043066485\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea221043066485\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">오늘 이수한의원에 환자분계서 내원하셨다</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">환자분이 허리가 좀 많이 아프셔서</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">요즘 거의 매일 오신다</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">저번주에</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">환자분이 일본에 여행을 다녀오셨는데</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\">한국에 돌아오면서 이수한의원 식구들 선물도 사오셨다</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/line_characters_in_love\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://storep-phinf.pstatic.net/line_characters_in_love/original_7.png?type=p50_50\" alt=\"line_characters_in_love-7\"></a>&nbsp;</div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><br /></div><div style=\"text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/MjAxNzA3MDNfNDkg/MDAxNDk5MDY4NDU1NDk4.TXOuJwIPr0dLhlL0Y-QNG1AvcYeu6uDDeDsUJ4KVepYg.f2WnJJffVqm3W8rjtxdKTbzZ-n-eM2qbfP-vISfCMLgg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20170703_161837292.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"550\" height=\"413\" style=\"cursor: pointer; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rwidth:550px; rheight:413px;\" id=\"MjAxNzA3MDNfNDkg/MDAxNDk5MDY4NDU1NDk4.TXOuJwIPr0dLhlL0Y-QNG1AvcYeu6uDDeDsUJ4KVepYg.f2WnJJffVqm3W8rjtxdKTbzZ-n-eM2qbfP-vISfCMLgg.JPEG.isuhani/KakaoTalk_20170703_161837292.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '900